-- How to configure Command line in Intillij IDEA
** open Setting (Ctrl + Alt + S) -- Tool Setting 
** shell path == C:\Windows\System32\WindowsPowerShell\v1.0\powershell.exe
** Apply -- Ok 

-- How to configure Git 
** configure OpenSSH -- check openSSh install or not .. In setting - add optional feature -- 
   set Env System variable -- path == C:\Windows\System32\OpenSSH   -- restart System 
** for checking OpenSSh == ssh -V

** ssh-keygen -t rsa -b 4096       -- generating ssh key pair 
** for save file location ENTER -- default location 
** set password like    == Sa***git***123
** ssh-add C:\Users\CS\.ssh\id_rsa     -- ssh key added local system
** cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub           -- to display ssh key 
** copy this SSH KEY -- Open Github Setting -- add SSH key -- set name -- paste ssh key okk 

  

